Trade/Device Name(s): FORA POCT S10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FORA POCT S10 Blood Glucose meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FORA POCT S10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary and venous whole blood using electrochemical biosensor method
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from the finger and venous whole blood samples for multiple patient use by health care professionals in health care facilities as an aid in monitoring diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes or use on neonates
